          "content": {
            "size": 1180,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "[{\"content\":\"I couldn’t fetch the customer analytics right now because the backend rejected the request. So I can’t reliably identify which customers are near their credit limit from the available data. Also, this workspace doesn’t expose a direct credit-limit or limit-utilization field, so I can only work from outstanding balance data once the report is available. If you want, I can next try: 1) highest outstanding customers, 2) a specific customer’s ledger, or 3) a narrower customer segment.\",\"additional_kwargs\":{},\"response_metadata\":{},\"type\":\"human\",\"name\":null,\"id\":\"befc6fbc-d39a-459f-b169-b8a5ad0e0894\"},{\"content\":\"Samajh gaya—main credit-limit/limit-utilization fields ke bina “near credit limit” ko reliably identify nahi kar paunga. Main aapke liye yeh business data dekh sakta hoon: (1) highest outstanding customers, (2) kisi specific customer ka ledger, ya (3) kisi segment ko narrow karke analytics—kaunsa option chahiye aur segment/Customer name ya code kya hai?\",\"additional_kwargs\":{},\"response_metadata\":{},\"type\":\"ai\",\"name\":null,\"id\":\"cea7505e-d37b-472c-aaf3-2edb93eb9b4e\",\"tool_calls\":[],\"invalid_tool_calls\":[],\"usage_metadata\":null}]"
